| Route | LiveView | Purpose |
|-------|----------|---------|
| `/chat` | ChatLive | Main chat + processing inspector |
| `/dashboard` | DashboardLive | System monitoring, GenServers, metrics |
| `/accuracy` | AccuracyLive | Model accuracy, confusion matrices, trends |
| `/explorer` | ExplorerLive | Training world data (entities, episodes, knowledge) |
| `/settings` | SettingsLive | World/entity management, ML training controls |
